27692.title: ARRDLogo1
27692.content: The Auld Reekie Roller Derby Logo: Green outline containing a star (pink overprint effect), a moon (yellow overprint effect), and a circle with a segment out of it (grey underprint). Text box under reads: AULD REEKIE ROLLER DERBY plus the founding date (2018) and Edinburgh.

27693.title: ARRDLogo2
27693.content: The "font bar" version of the logo: green outline rectangle contains "AULD REEKIE ROLLER DERBY" and "20 EDINBURGH 08". A outline star, with pink overprint effect, sits between "Auld" and "Reekie"

27694.content: A collection of elements and alternate versions of the Auld Reekie Roller Derby logo.
